# Mosquitto password file — DO NOT commit the real passwd file.
# Generate it with:
#   mosquitto_passwd -c -b docker/mosquitto/passwd iot-backend <your-password>
#   mosquitto_passwd -b    docker/mosquitto/passwd iot-simulator <your-password>
#
# Format (bcrypt hashes, not plaintext — safe to inspect but not to share):
# iot-backend:$7$...
# iot-simulator:$7$...
